4e74d28d-c7a9-4a25-8796-242cfb128893.title: Assassin's Creed
4e74d28d-c7a9-4a25-8796-242cfb128893.summary: Experience an epic historical action-adventure story set in feudal Japan! Become a lethal shinobi Assassin and a powerful legendary samurai as you explore a beautiful open world in a time of chaos. Switch seamlessly between two unlikely allies as you discover their common destiny and usher in a new era for Japan.

00cb531b-8ae8-44b6-9b1c-5e218d4d8a27.summary: Call of Duty: Mobile (formerly known as Call of Duty: Legends of War, and Elite Squad in its pre-alpha phase) is a free-to-play mobile first-person shooter that was released first in Alpha on December 15th, 2018 for Android systems only in Australia.[
